  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To prospectively investigate the effect of transjugular intrahepatic portosystemic shunt
      (TIPS) on oxygenation in cirrhotic patients with hepatopulmonary syndrome (HPS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
